name: Carlos Barnes
description: A Simple Guy, Living A Simple Life, Looking For A Simple Girl To Complete The Picture. Some Would Say I’m Old Fashioned, I Prefer to Think of It as Having Traditional Beliefs. Things Such As Romance, Chivalry And Respect, Are Important Aspects Of My Life While There Are ‘People’ Here Who Are Not What And Who They Are Pretending To Be, And Are Not Serious In Finding A Lifelong Mate – Understand Clearly That Such Is Not The Case With Me.
